&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : if you know me ) is a 2015 indian tamil-language neo-noir crime-drama film co-written and directed by gautham menon , and produced by a. m. rathnam . the film stars ajith kumar , arun vijay , trisha krishnan , anushka shetty , parvathy nair and vivek . the soundtrack album and background score for the film was composed by harris jayaraj . the film was edited by anthony while dan macarthur handled the cinematography . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; 's story follows the journey of man named &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , from the age of 13 till the age of 38 . it is also the final film of menon 's police trilogy of films that began with kaakha kaakha ( 2003 ) and continued with &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 2006 ) . the film was released on 5 february 2015 .